### Homogeniety Test
Where data has been provided for a Homogeneity test the following results were recorded:

|Property                   |Value                                |
|---------------------------|-------------------------------------|
|Alpha Value                |`r params$homogeneityTestAlphaValue` |
|Degrees of Freedom Within  |`r params$homogeneityTestDofW`       |
|Degrees of Freedom Between |`r params$homogeneityTestDofB`       |
|F Statistic                |`r params$homogeneityTestFStat`      |
|F Critical                 |`r params$homogeneityTestFCrit`      |

#### **Result: `r params$homogeneityTestResult`**
***
